Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.60,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\fs90\pos(960,347.8)\3c&HC3C3C3&}YEAR 2000, ANTARCTICA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the super solenoid theory\Nthat Dr. Katsuragi proposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That theory is just too radical!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing more than a hypothesis\Nat this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But only the S2 theory can explain\Nthat giant’s power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.70,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Ikari and his team are apparently\Nleaving on the 11th.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.99,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish they’d set up the smoking\Narea a bit closer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We don’t even need to measure it\Nto know it’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.75,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard there was talk of making the\Nentire facility smoke-free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it existed in our reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.12,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should be glad there is one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have no choice but to acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.50,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they’d done that, I wouldn’t be here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.59,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’ll accept it when all the data’s been verified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Scientists put too much faith\Nin their own ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.76,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about the Lance of Longinus?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re a self-righteous kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:31.76,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It’s been sitting there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They become fixated too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.26,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}since it was shipped here last week\Nfrom the Dead Sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re incapable of accurately\Nassessing reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:37.64,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will be treated before it’s sent\Nunderground, won’t it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are the ones seeking\Nto find the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:38.76,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are we okay on that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.47,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The contact experiment with the donor{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s quite ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:42.98,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is scheduled for the 13th of next month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not so noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.94,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We’ll be able to make the\Nadjustments in time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Discovery is joy and understanding\Nis dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:50.98,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today’s experiment is on the ego threshold\Nsignal of that field, was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All they seek is self-gratification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppress the surface radiation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s over the projected limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.11,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Emergency situation! Emergency situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The DNA that was inserted into Adam\Nis already physically fused!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:57.95,Default Top,,0,0,0,,All staff, get in your protective gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All workers in Level 2 and below,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,immediately evacuate to the upper area\Nof Central Dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.24,Default Top,,0,0,0,,All AT Fields are being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lance! Pull the Lance back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.79,Default Top,,0,0,0,,It’s no good! We can’t maintain\Nthe magnetic field!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s sinking in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t care if it only makes\Na small difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the damage to an absolute minimum!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The atomic components are breaking up\Nat the quark level! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin thermal dampening treatment\Nas soon as the Door of Gaf opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t care if it’s only for point one seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! It’s begun to walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it to use up as much of its anti-AT\NField energy as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The conversion system has already been set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Countdown commencing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s spreading its wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s breaking towards the surface!
